rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey,
what's that huge thing in the harbor?

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0002
rows.name: Ah, that is the Empire's Royal Ship.

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0004
rows.name:
I get it.
The size of the ship is a reflection
of the nation's strength.

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0005
rows.name:
Since we're here,
why don't we all go aboard?

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0006
rows.name:
No way!
I'm no good with all that formal stuff.
I can't even swallow fancy court food.

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0007
rows.name:
If you'd like,
I can have them prepare
some food from your homeland...

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0008
rows.name:
I appreciate it, but I'll pass.
Let's go, Kasumi!

rows.label: fev11_240_175_msg0010
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Her disposition of disliking
formality... it doesn't seem like
it's going to be cured...
